<scroll-view scroll-y class="scrollPage">
  <view class="UCenter-bg">
    <image src="/images/logo.png" class="png" mode="widthFix"></image>
    <view class="text-xl">智能互联
      <text class="text-df">v1.0</text>
    </view>
    <image src="/images/wave.gif" mode="scaleToFill" class="gif-wave"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="padding flex text-center text-grey bg-white shadow-warp">
<scroll-view scroll-x class="bg-white nav" scroll-with-animation scroll-left="{{scrollLeft}}">
  <view class="cu-item {{index==TabCur?'text-green cur':''}}" wx:for="{{10}}" wx:key bindtap="tabSelect" data-id="{{index}}">
    Tab{{index}}
  </view>
</scroll-view>
  </view>
   <view class="cu-bar bg-white solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class="action">
      <text class="cuIcon-title text-orange"></text> 宫格列表
    </view>
    <view class="action">
      <button class="cur-button.ny bg-green" size="mini" bindtap="showModal" data-target="gridModal">设置</button>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="cu-modal {{modalName=='gridModal'?'show':''}}" bindtap="hideModal">
    <view class="cu-dialog" catchtap>
      <radio-group class="block" bindchange="gridchange">
        <view class="cu-list menu text-left">
          <view class="cu-item" wx:for="{{3}}" wx:key>
            <label class="flex justify-between align-center flex-sub">
              <view class="flex-sub">{{index +3}} 列</view>
              <radio class="round" value="{{index +3}}" checked="{{gridCol==index+3}}"></radio>
            </label>
          </view>
        </view>
      </radio-group>
      <view class="cu-list menu text-left solid-top">
        <view class="cu-item">
          <view class="content">
            <text class="text-grey">边框</text>
          </view>
          <view class="action">
            <switch bindchange="gridswitch"></switch>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="cu-list grid col-{{gridCol}} {{gridBorder?'':'no-border'}}">
    <view class="cu-item" wx:for="{{iconList}}" wx:key wx:if="{{index<gridCol*2}}">
      <view class="cuIcon-{{item.icon}} text-{{item.color}}">
        <view class="cu-tag badge" wx:if="{{item.badge!=0}}">
          <block wx:if="{{item.badge!=1}}">{{item.badge>99?"99+":item.badge}}</block>
        </view>
      </view>
      <text>{{item.name}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-white solid-bottom margin-top">
  <view class="action">
    <text class="cuIcon-title text-blue"></text>资讯类
  </view>
</view>
<view class="cu-card dynamic {{isCard?'no-card':''}}">
  <view class="cu-item shadow">
    <view class="cu-list menu-avatar">
      <view class="cu-item">
        <view class="cu-avatar round lg" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10006.jpg);"></view>
        <view class="content flex-sub">
          <view>凯尔</view>
          <view class="text-gray text-sm flex justify-between">
            2019年12月3日
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="text-content">
      北汽集团党委副书记、总经理，福田汽车集团董事长张夕勇一行到福田戴姆勒调研指导并现场慰问！
    </view>
    <view class="grid flex-sub padding-lr {{isCard?'col-3 grid-square':'col-1'}}">
      <view class="bg-img {{isCard?'':'only-img'}}" style="background-image:url(https://tse4-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP.6mA5ZoGprFhBv4OwXgDecQHaE8?w=282&h=188&c=7&o=5&pid=1.7);" wx:for="{{isCard?9:1}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="text-gray text-sm text-right padding">
      <text class="cuIcon-attentionfill margin-lr-xs"></text> 10
      <text class="cuIcon-appreciatefill margin-lr-xs"></text> 20
      <text class="cuIcon-messagefill margin-lr-xs"></text> 30
    </view> 
  </view>
</view>

<view class="cu-card case {{isCard?'no-card':''}}">
  <view class="cu-item shadow">
    <view class="image">
      <image src="https://tse2-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP.dGGfVgusW-y1urFsH5tLCAHaE7?w=282&h=187&c=7&o=5&pid=1.7" mode="widthFix"></image>
      <view class="cu-tag bg-blue">最新</view>
      <view class="cu-bar bg-shadeBottom">
        <text class="text-cut">1月7日下午，以“共建 共享 共赢——致力于专业的项目管理”为主题的蓝天保卫战项目经验总结会在新办公楼B313会议室举行。产品规划、产品工程、采购、</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

 <view class="cu-bar bg-white solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class="action">
      <text class="cuIcon-title text-yellow"></text> 调研类
    </view>
  </view>
<view class="cu-list grid col-{{questionCol}} {{gridBorder?'':'no-border'}}">
    <view class="cu-item" wx:for="{{questList}}" wx:key wx:if="{{index<questionCol*2}}">
      <view class="cuIcon-{{item.icon}} text-{{item.color}}">
        <view class="cu-tag badge" wx:if="{{item.badge!=0}}">
          <block wx:if="{{item.badge!=1}}">{{item.badge>99?"99+":item.badge}}</block>
        </view>
      </view>
      <text>{{item.name}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
 <view class="cu-bar bg-white solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class="action">
    <text class="cuIcon-appreciatefill text-red"></text>
    <text class="text-grey">赞赏支持</text>
     <view class="action padding-xl">  
     <text class="text-green"> by:车联网科</text>
    </view>
    </view>
  </view>


  <view class="cu-bar bg-white solid-bottom margin-top">
  </view>
</view>
</scroll-view>
